com.gwtplatform.mvp.client

Interface UiHandlers

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CarsUiHandlers, CarUiHandlers, EditManufacturerUiHandlers, EditRatingUiHandlers, HeaderUiHandlers, LoginUiHandlers, ManufacturerDetailUiHandlers, ManufacturerUiHandlers, NavigationUiHandlers, RatingDetailUiHandlers, RatingUiHandlers, StatisticsUiHandlers
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CarPresenter, CarsPresenter, EditManufacturerPresenter, EditRatingPresenter, HeaderPresenter, LoginPresenter, ManufacturerDetailPresenter, ManufacturerPresenter, NavigationTabPresenter, RatingDetailPresenter, RatingPresenter, StatisticsPresenter

    public interface UiHandlers
    Use this marker interface on classes that implement the controls required by a View to communicate back with its Presenter or PresenterWidget.
    Author:
    Christian Goudreau
